                  2025's leading systems process not just text, but images, charts, diagrams, videos, and audio content. This comprehensive understanding enables retrieval based on visual elements, data trends in charts, or specific information mentioned in recorded meetings.
                </p>
                <ul class="text-white text-sm space-y-1 ml-4">
                  <li>• OCR with 99.5%+ accuracy for scanned documents</li>
                  <li>• Chart and graph data extraction</li>
                  <li>• Video content transcription and indexing</li>
                  <li>• Image recognition and categorization</li>
